NAME

  IOas::SJIS2004 - provides SJIS2004 I/O subroutines for UTF-8 script

SYNOPSIS

  use IOas::SJIS2004;

DESCRIPTION

  IOas::SJIS2004 module provides SJIS2004 I/O subroutines for UTF-8 script for
  stable scripting environment, using no utf8 pragma, no UTF-8 flag.

SUBROUTINES

  Octet Length as I/O Encoding
    IOas::SJIS2004::length($utf8str)
    IOas::SJIS2004::sprintf($utf8format, @utf8list)
    IOas::SJIS2004::substr($utf8expr, $offset_as_cp932x, $length_as_cp932x, $utf8replacement)

  String Comparison as I/O Encoding
    IOas::SJIS2004::cmp($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::eq($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::ne($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::ge($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::gt($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::le($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::lt($utf8str_a, $utf8str_b)
    IOas::SJIS2004::sort(@utf8str)

  Encoding Convert on I/O Operations
    IOas::SJIS2004::getc(FILEHANDLE)
    IOas::SJIS2004::readline(FILEHANDLE)
    IOas::SJIS2004::print(FILEHANDLE, @utf8str)
    IOas::SJIS2004::printf(FILEHANDLE, $utf8format, @utf8list)

SUPPORTED PERL VERSIONS

  perl version 5.005_03 to newest perl

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/
